MoldingInfo.Description: hot pressed at unspecified temperature and then isobarically cooled

Additive.Description: post-press curing of the matrix under vacuum (hardening/curing agent/additive was already in the matrix)

Dielectric_and_Impedance_Spectroscopy_An.Equipment: Novocontrol Alpha Analyzer (type K) in combination with a Novocontrol active BDS-1200 sample cell
Dielectric_and_Impedance_Spectroscopy_An.Description: Measurements were performed on circularly laminar samples  of 0.5 mm thickness with sputtered gold electrodes (15 nm thick) on both sides, at multiple temperatures

Differential_Scanning_Calorimetry.Description: 2 cycles with the following ramps were performed and the second cycle was used for calculations/measurements with ~ 5 mg og materials and for four specimens.
Differential_Scanning_Calorimetry.CycleInformation: Dwell time of 5 minutes at 150 Celsius is used after the sample is heated to 150 Celsius

Pulsed_Electro_Acoustic.Equipment: Novocontrol Alpha Analyzer (type K) in combination with a Novocontrol active BDS-1200 sample cell
